import React from "react";
import {
    FormGroup,
    FormControl,
    Input,
    InputLabel,
    FormHelperText,
    Grid,
    Box,
} from "@material-ui/core";

const Registro = () => {
    return (
        <Grid container>
            <Grid item xs-12>
                <Box bgcolor="#FFFFFF" p={10}>
                    <FormGroup>
                        <FormControl>
                            <InputLabel htmlFor="my-input">
                                Email address
                            </InputLabel>
                            <Input
                                id="my-input"
                                aria-describedby="my-helper-text"
                            />
                            <FormHelperText id="my-helper-text">
                                We'll never share your email.
                            </FormHelperText>
                        </FormControl>

                        <FormControl>
                            <InputLabel htmlFor="my-input">Email </InputLabel>
                            <Input
                                id="my-input"
                                aria-describedby="my-helper-text"
                            />
                            <FormHelperText id="my-helper-text">
                                We'll never share your email.
                            </FormHelperText>
                        </FormControl>
                    </FormGroup>
                </Box>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    );
};

export default Registro;
